      "[TIP] Elevate your guest experience by implementing seamless, tech-enabled RSVP and concierge services, ensuring VIPs feel valued before they even arrive at the venue.",
      "**Step 1 — Register on the GEA Portal:** Your company must be registered on the GEA Lichaat platform (lichaat.gea.gov.sa). You will need a valid Saudi commercial registration (CR) and Absher/Nafath authentication.",
      "**Step 2 — Prepare Your Application Documents:** Required documents include: detailed event brief (event type, date, time, location, expected attendance), signed venue contract, technical safety plan, artist/performer GEA licenses, security plan, and emergency evacuation plan.",
      "**Step 3 — Submit Your Application:** Submit through the GEA portal at least 4–8 weeks before your event date. High-profile events and those with international artists may require 10–12 weeks.",
